title: About Me
text:
Welcome to my portfolio! I’m a data analyst currently seeking remote work opportunities in the climate industry. I have over 4 years of experience spanning data analytics, consulting, and business operations.
I use this site to post summaries of my latest side projects and learnings. Feel free to connect with me on LinkedIn and let me know what you think.
